1
00:00:14,090 --> 00:00:20,390
♪Suddenly, you showed up♪

2
00:00:22,150 --> 00:00:28,750
♪Who stole away those years♪

3
00:00:30,600 --> 00:00:37,320
♪Oh, night and day♪

4
00:00:38,760 --> 00:00:45,540
♪Oh, it's been a long time♪

5
00:00:45,930 --> 00:00:50,050
♪Pass through the bustling world
in the daytime♪

6
00:00:50,050 --> 00:00:53,880
♪Circumvent love at night♪

7
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:57,760
♪Day after day, year after year♪

8
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:02,040
♪I wake up and close my eyes
before it gets dark♪

9
00:01:02,040 --> 00:01:06,140
♪But when the day breaks into the night♪

10
00:01:06,140 --> 00:01:10,220
♪It makes me believe
that there's still love♪

11
00:01:10,220 --> 00:01:14,050
♪If you want it, if I want it♪

12
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:20,800
♪It's a vow of night and day♪

13
00:01:26,520 --> 00:01:32,890
♪It's a vow of day and night♪

14
00:01:32,890 --> 00:01:37,200
[Blooming]

15
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:39,920
[Episode 27]

16
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,080
Zhao Tantan.

17
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:52,200
How dare you!

18
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:54,320
You've got some nerve sneaking into
the secret vault to steal the lotus seeds.

19
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,040
Step away.

20
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,680
What punishment do you think
you deserve?

21
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,600
Master.

22
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:59,360
I just want to touch the lotus seeds
in advance.

23
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,320
I didn't mean anything else.

24
00:02:00,320 --> 00:02:02,520
Stop scolding me.

25
00:02:09,910 --> 00:02:13,280
Well, you guys ganged up on me.

26
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,360
It's Senior Mu Bai's idea.

27
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:16,680
Your hand.

28
00:02:21,880 --> 00:02:22,520
[The Light of Qingyuan]

29
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,240
I carved it myself. Do you like it?

30
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,080
Yes.

31
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:27,800
Give it to me.

32
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:31,880
Give me your hand.

33
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,800
[The Light of Qingyuan]

34
00:02:35,160 --> 00:02:37,680
The official certification
as the Light of Qingyuan.

35
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,920
From now on, you're my person.

36
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:41,040
Give me a kiss.

37
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:42,760
Hold on.

38
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,760
Why don't you just kill me
to make it more exciting?

39
00:02:45,080 --> 00:02:45,800
That's too much.

40
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,920
You can have fun when you're back.

41
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,880
Let's get down to business first.

42
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:51,600
Every time you touch the lotus seed,

43
00:02:51,720 --> 00:02:53,040
you'll briefly lose consciousness.

44
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:55,000
In case of accidents at the ceremony,

45
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:57,200
I've specially invited Master here
to protect you.

46
00:02:58,920 --> 00:02:59,520
Go ahead.

47
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:08,960
So, the new room, the flexible feast,

48
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,560
the lotus seeds, and this seal

49
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,280
were prepared by you in advance.

50
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,440
It's Senior Mu Bai
who prepared these things.

51
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,760
Do you like them?

52
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:18,720
Yes.

53
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,400
I love them!

54
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,160
Hold on.

55
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,600
I also made a contribution.

56
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,640
Come on.

57
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,680
Master.

58
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:26,640
I like you too.

59
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:27,600
That's great.

60
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:29,480
Touch the lotus seeds.

61
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,120
Okay.

62
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,560
Master.

63
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,080
Did you bring the right lotus seeds?

64
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,720
Do you know which two I should touch?

65
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:42,120
I'm not a dotard.

66
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,080
You've touched the one in Wangfang City.

67
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,400
You need to touch two lotus seeds now.

68
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,240
One is left for you by Mu Xuan,

69
00:03:47,320 --> 00:03:49,880
the other is the one we already have.

70
00:03:50,120 --> 00:03:50,760
Is that right?

71
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:52,360
Hurry up and touch them.

72
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,840
If I have Dacheng Skill

73
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:59,160
after touching them,

74
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,120
it'll be my turn to protect you.

75
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:02,640
I'd like that.

76
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:11,440
Tantan!

77
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:11,920
Tantan!

78
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:13,520
Is she okay?

79
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:14,880
The lotus seeds' spiritual power
is so strong

80
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,920
that her internal energy
goes disorganized.

81
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:17,240
I'll take her back to rest.

82
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:18,440
Okay.

83
00:04:21,510 --> 00:04:23,080
The Seven-Leaf Lotus is gone.

84
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,080
You're a thief!

85
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:24,920
You're a thief!

86
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,120
- A thief!
- A thief!

87
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:27,040
You're a thief!

88
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:27,760
You're a thief!

89
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:29,520
- A thief!
- A thief!

90
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,080
I didn't.

91
00:04:30,080 --> 00:04:31,280
Are you gonna cover up her?

92
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,480
She's a spirit.

93
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:33,280
A liar!

94
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,080
A thief!

95
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,200
Mu Bai, kill her.

96
00:04:35,480 --> 00:04:36,720
The good cannot coexist with the bad.

97
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,120
You two can't be together.

98
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:40,120
You're a cultivator. She's a spirit.

99
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,080
Kill her!

100
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,080
Kill her!

101
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,480
Kill her!

102
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,240
Kill her!

103
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,360
Kill her!

104
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,160
Kill her!

105
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,240
Yes, she's a spirit!

106
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:47,800
Kill her!

107
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,440
Kill her!

108
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:49,520
Kill her!

109
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,640
Kill her!

110
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:51,400
Shut up!

111
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:57,880
Why don't you speak up for me?

112
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,640
You said you would always trust me.

113
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,640
Lian, this is not a joke.

114
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,560
The Seven-Leaf Lotus is important
to the Qingyuan Sect

115
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:07,160
and to the whole world.

116
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:12,920
You don't trust me.

117
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:16,440
So what if I stole it?

118
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,320
She's admitted it.

119
00:05:17,320 --> 00:05:17,760
It's her.

120
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:18,240
It's her.

121
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,800
Am I less important
than a magic instrument?

122
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:20,480
It's her.

123
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,640
Is your love for me so vulnerable?

124
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,520
It's not the time to be childish.

125
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:27,800
If the Lotus gets into the world,
it will be sought after by everyone,

126
00:05:27,880 --> 00:05:28,920
which will bring disaster to the world.

127
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,560
Mu Bai.

128
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,160
Why waste time on a spirit

129
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:32,200
who stole things?

130
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,760
Lotus Spirit,
hand over the Seven-Leaf Lotus.

131
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,560
Otherwise, we won't spare you.

132
00:05:36,640 --> 00:05:40,480
- Hand it over!
- Hand it over!

133
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,160
Hand it over!

134
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:49,040
- Hand it over!
- Hand it over!

135
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,840
Mu Bai.

136
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:50,640
Lian Wen.

137
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:55,080
- Hand it over!
- Hand it over!

138
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:06,040
Tantan, you're awake.

139
00:06:06,280 --> 00:06:07,200
How are you feeling?

140
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:09,040
Tantan?

141
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,440
What's wrong?

142
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:16,640
Mu Bai, after I touched the lotus seeds,

143
00:06:16,960 --> 00:06:19,440
I saw your past with Lian Wen.

144
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,800
It felt so real,

145
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,480
as if I had been there with you.

146
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:28,320
Tantan, don't think too much about it.

147
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:30,760
What happened between Lian Wen and I
is in the past.

148
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,080
But

149
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:44,720
you still had a relationship
with her, didn't you?

150
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,880
And you failed her.

151
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,040
About Lian Wen,

152
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,760
I thought I'd made it clear.

153
00:06:55,320 --> 00:06:57,200
Are you doubting my love for you?

154
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,960
I'll ask you one more time.

155
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:06,480
Do you feel you owe something
to Lian Wen?

156
00:07:06,640 --> 00:07:07,480
If she and I show up in front of you

157
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,520
at the same time,

158
00:07:09,640 --> 00:07:10,800
who would you choose?

159
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,680
Now or in the future,

160
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:21,760
all I can see and care about

161
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:24,000
is only you, Zhao Tantan.

162
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:28,320
Very good.

163
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:36,000
Tantan, we should keep our distance.

164
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,880
Dabai, I'm tired.

165
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,560
I want to rest.

166
00:07:46,520 --> 00:07:48,240
Do you need Huai Meng
to take a look at you?

167
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:50,360
It's okay. I'm fine.

168
00:07:51,440 --> 00:07:52,960
Okay, I'll leave.

169
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,120
Where am I?

170
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,120
Let me out!

171
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,440
Let me out!

172
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,480
Let me out!

173
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:08,840
Lian Wen?

174
00:08:09,720 --> 00:08:10,640
Are you Lian Wen?

175
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,920
Yes. We've finally met.

176
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:17,960
Where is this place?

177
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,600
This is your consciousness.

178
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,760
How did you get in?

179
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:24,360
The seven lotus seeds
carry my consciousness.

180
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:26,400
After you touched the lotus seeds,

181
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:30,240
my consciousness awakened in your body.

182
00:08:32,190 --> 00:08:33,160
Let me out!

183
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:34,640
Let me out!

184
00:08:35,800 --> 00:08:38,000
Zhao Tantan, you used my appearance

185
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:40,440
and enjoyed too much love
that should have belonged to me.

186
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:43,830
Now I want you to stay here

187
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,040
and feel my hatred.

188
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:45,960
What do you want to do?

189
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,240
What do you want to do?

190
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,680
What do I want to do?

191
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,560
I want you to watch

192
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:56,360
how I'm going to finish
what happened 100 years ago.

193
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,680
Mu Bai, and the Demon Lord.

194
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:03,200
All these people have to die one by one!

195
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,240
Don't go!

196
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:05,840
Let me out!

197
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,560
Let me out!

198
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,960
Let me out!

199
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,560
(There is something wrong with Tantan)

200
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,160
(after she touched the lotus seeds
and woke up.)

201
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:18,280
(Her look and tone were strange.)

202
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,800
But

203
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:23,680
you still had a relationship
with her, didn't you?

204
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:43,240
Tantan?

205
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:51,560
Why are you here?

206
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,600
Mu Xuan, it's me.

207
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:58,000
I'm Lian Wen.

208
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,600
Lian Wen?

209
00:10:01,360 --> 00:10:02,320
How could that be?

210
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:04,840
I was killed by Cui Chen with his sword.

211
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:07,400
Today Zhao Tantan
touched all the lotus seeds,

212
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,720
so I woke up.

213
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,120
Where's Zhao Tantan?

214
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,640
Don't worry.

215
00:10:13,320 --> 00:10:14,240
She's fine.

216
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:24,880
Is this me?

217
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,800
Of course it's you.

218
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:29,960
I carved the wood

219
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,400
to remember your face.

220
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,800
With it by my side,

221
00:10:33,280 --> 00:10:34,480
it's like having you with me.

222
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:37,040
If I had chosen you 100 years ago,

223
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:39,920
there wouldn't have been
so much pain, right?

224
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:42,800
I failed to protect you back then.

225
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,440
But if I were Cui Chen,

226
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,160
I would never let anyone hurt you.

227
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:49,440
I don't blame you.
I chose the wrong person.

228
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,760
Lian Wen, now that you're back,

229
00:10:53,160 --> 00:10:55,080
just let go of the past
and give me a chance.

230
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:56,360
I'll make you happy.

231
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:58,280
No one can hurt you again.

232
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:04,080
If Zhao Tantan and I

233
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,760
appear in front of you at the same time,

234
00:11:06,360 --> 00:11:07,040
who would you choose?

235
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:11,720
I've been looking for you
in the past 100 years.

236
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:13,920
I never thought about giving up.

237
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,040
So, don't ask me that question.

238
00:11:16,960 --> 00:11:17,800
It's always you.

239
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:29,120
Mu Xuan,
only your love for me is genuine.

240
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,960
I won't fail you.

241
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:44,120
I came back this time

242
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:46,560
because
I have something important to do,

243
00:11:46,920 --> 00:11:47,880
and I need your help.

244
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,240
What do you need me to do?

245
00:11:53,560 --> 00:11:55,920
Take back all the lotus seeds
and kill Cui Chen.

246
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,280
Kill Cui Chen?

247
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:58,800
Don't you want that?

248
00:11:59,240 --> 00:12:00,880
A hundred years ago,
you were trodden under feet.

249
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:01,840
Have you forgotten that?

250
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:04,360
(I promised the Demon Lord
not to kill Cui Chen,)

251
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,560
(just to bring Lian Wen back to life.)

252
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,800
(Now she's back.)

253
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,000
(I don't need to keep my promise.)

254
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,120
Of course I haven't forgotten.

255
00:12:14,560 --> 00:12:15,520
How do you want to do it?

256
00:12:33,480 --> 00:12:34,440
Why are you here?

257
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:35,600
Where have you been?

258
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,400
Didn't you say you were tired
and wanted to rest?

259
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:40,920
I lay down but couldn't sleep.

260
00:12:41,400 --> 00:12:42,800
So, I thought of finding Hu Meng

261
00:12:42,800 --> 00:12:44,240
and getting a bottle of aged wine

262
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,640
to help me sleep.

263
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,200
Since you're here,

264
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:49,080
have a drink with me.

265
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,960
You just woke up. You shouldn't drink.

266
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,920
Life is short.
We should have a good time.

267
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:58,040
Don't leave the glass empty
in the moonlight.

268
00:12:58,800 --> 00:13:00,000
I'll be made

269
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,720
the Light of Qingyuan in two days.

270
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:04,000
Isn't it worth celebrating?

271
00:13:05,200 --> 00:13:07,480
Come on, have a drink with me.

272
00:14:01,160 --> 00:14:02,040
Mu Xuan?

273
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,080
What are you looking for?

274
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:06,600
Nothing.

275
00:14:07,920 --> 00:14:10,160
Master, I want to tell you something.

276
00:14:10,240 --> 00:14:11,080
What is it?

277
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,920
I dare not forget every move
you taught me.

278
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:15,760
You little brat.

279
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:22,800
