into the lotus seedpod.

579
00:32:38,120 --> 00:32:40,040
Why can't
I restore the Seven-Leaf Lotus?

580
00:32:42,240 --> 00:32:42,880
Uncle.

581
00:32:43,000 --> 00:32:44,400
Uncle, your Strange Tales
in the Secular World

582
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,640
has recorded a lot of things.

583
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:46,320
Isn't there anything

584
00:32:46,320 --> 00:32:47,960
about how to turn the lotus seeds
into a lotus?

585
00:32:48,160 --> 00:32:49,000
Oh, no!

586
00:32:49,000 --> 00:32:51,000
Cui Chen's spiritual power is declining!

587
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:51,760
Let me do it.

588
00:33:03,680 --> 00:33:04,760
His spiritual power

589
00:33:05,560 --> 00:33:07,160
has dropped from the seventh level
of Dacheng Skill

590
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:09,360
to the fifth level of Enlightenment.

591
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,120
He...

592
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:13,960
Will it keep dropping?

593
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:15,600
Based on his condition,

594
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,120
it will.

595
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:24,440
If

596
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:26,600
he loses all his spiritual power,

597
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:29,000
what will happen?

598
00:33:31,000 --> 00:33:32,720
He'll turn into a mortal.

599
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,080
At his age,

600
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:36,760
he won't last long

601
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,680
before he dies.

602
00:33:38,800 --> 00:33:39,240
Then...

603
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:41,840
Doesn't it mean
he'll end up like Zhu Yan?

604
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:46,480
Well...

605
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:49,240
If we can't lift the Xilan Flower Curse,

606
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:50,840
is there any way

607
00:33:50,840 --> 00:33:52,680
to slow down the fading
of his spiritual power?

608
00:33:53,240 --> 00:33:55,720
No matter what kind of
magic instrument or elixir he needs,

609
00:33:55,720 --> 00:33:58,000
I'll risk my life to get it.

610
00:33:58,080 --> 00:33:58,720
How about this,

611
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,840
I'll make some Essence-Stabilizing Soup
for Cui Chen first.

612
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,240
But it can only

613
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:04,000
temporarily prevent his weakness.

614
00:34:04,040 --> 00:34:05,120
I can't stop

615
00:34:05,280 --> 00:34:06,840
the decline of his spiritual power.

616
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,160
What should I do?

617
00:34:12,600 --> 00:34:13,480
Do I have to

618
00:34:13,480 --> 00:34:15,640
watch him die?

619
00:34:15,840 --> 00:34:17,120
What should I do?

620
00:34:17,120 --> 00:34:18,600
Master, what should I do?

621
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,750
Tantan, calm down.

622
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:21,190
Tantan, calm down.

623
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:22,560
Tantan, don't worry.

624
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,230
Aren't there tens of thousands of books

625
00:34:25,320 --> 00:34:26,480
in our library?

626
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,080
Don't worry.

627
00:34:27,080 --> 00:34:29,000
Even if I have to stay up all night,
not eating or drinking,

628
00:34:29,120 --> 00:34:30,270
I'll still read them all

629
00:34:30,400 --> 00:34:30,840
and find a way

630
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:32,270
to save Cui Chen.

631
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:34,190
I'll check the Strange Tales
in the Secular World.

632
00:34:34,190 --> 00:34:34,920
Huai Meng.

633
00:34:35,040 --> 00:34:36,120
Don't let me fall asleep this time.

634
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:37,320
You can pull my hair

635
00:34:37,320 --> 00:34:38,840
or pinch my ass to keep me awake.

636
00:34:38,960 --> 00:34:39,600
I will.

637
00:34:39,670 --> 00:34:40,360
I will.

638
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:40,600
I will.

639
00:34:40,600 --> 00:34:42,400
Tantan, you can't collapse.

640
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:44,230
All of us will help you, right?

641
00:34:44,880 --> 00:34:45,400
Right?

642
00:34:59,120 --> 00:35:00,120
I'm sorry.

643
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:02,000
I lost control of my emotions.

644
00:35:02,520 --> 00:35:03,920
There's no such thing
as losing control of your emotions.

645
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:06,080
Anyone would be worried about
Cui Chen's situation.

646
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:08,120
You're not losing control.

647
00:35:08,600 --> 00:35:09,520
It's okay.

648
00:35:10,120 --> 00:35:12,960
Tantan,
it's normal that you feel this way.

649
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:14,520
If you don't lose control
of your emotions,

650
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:16,000
that would be strange.

651
00:35:22,400 --> 00:35:23,840
Thank you.

652
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:12,480
When I was in a coma,

653
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:17,040
were you also worried like this?

654
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,400
You know what,

655
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:24,800
I thought

656
00:36:25,680 --> 00:36:27,920
that by collecting all the lotus seeds,

657
00:36:28,600 --> 00:36:30,920
I could restore the Seven-Leaf Lotus

658
00:36:31,600 --> 00:36:34,680
and lift your Xilan Flower Curse.

659
00:36:36,960 --> 00:36:40,120
But I didn't expect
my hopes to be dashed.

660
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:43,840
But...

661
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:45,840
But it doesn't matter.

662
00:36:47,120 --> 00:36:49,200
I'll find a way,

663
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,160
even if

664
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:55,200
it means I have to stay away from you
for the rest of my life

